independent charismatic Lakewood Church. She was hospitalized in good 
condition. Police Sgt. J. C. Mosier described the device as "some sort of pipe 
bomb." A spokesman for the federal Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco and Firearms said 
it was doubtful that there was any link to recent bomb attacks that killed a 
judge and a lawyer. 
