<DOCID> 169443 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 31, 1990, Wednesday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 5; Sports Desk 
</P>
