<P>
Photo, Mike Wolf of Harvard, center, breaks free for a layup as Notre Dame's 
Kirk Miller (10) can only watch during the Saracens' 71-60 victory. MIKE 
SERGIEFF / For The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
