<HEADLINE>
<P>
DIGEST: SYLMAR TO STAGE BASEBALL FUND-RAISER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Sylmar High Baseball Alumni Assn. will sponsor a golf tournament 
fund-raiser at El Cariso Golf Course in Sylmar on Feb. 23. 
</P>
<P>
Proceeds will go toward the establishment of a college scholarship for a Sylmar 
ballplayer. 
</P>
<P>
The $40 cost includes greens fees, golf cart and prizes. 
</P>
<P>
Information: 818-367-1971. 
</P>
