<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: POP/ROCK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By SHAUNA SNOW, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Soul Train Hosts: Luther Vandross will join Dionne Warwick and Patti LaBelle as 
hosts of the fourth annual Soul Train Music Awards, to be telecast live from 
the Shrine Auditorium on March 14. The program, which honors the top artists in 
R&amp;B, soul, gospel and rap categories, will air in Los Angeles on KTTV 
Channel 11. SHAUNA SNOW 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
