PUBLISHING INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; JOURNALISM; REPORTERS; MARKETING; 
ADVERTISING; DEFORD, FRANK; PRICE, PETER; AZCARRAGA, EMILIO; NEWS MEDIA -- 
UNITED STATES 
</P>
